      "content": "A meeting might be overkill. The devs are pretty confident the new engine's logic rules will cover most edge cases. Besides, the whole point of the switch is to move away from the \"black box\" approach of LLMs. We need something more predictable and less reliant on subjective \"nuance.\" Why do you think the new system won't be able to handle those context issues?",
